dc_description_s: Scale 1:13,000,000 (E 90°41ʹ00ʺ--E 97°55ʹ00ʺ/N 28°00ʹ00ʺ--N 15°00ʹ00ʺ). Relief shown pictorially. Shows roads, railroads, lighthouses, passes, forts, and administrative divisions. On verso: French text, entitled: Description de Bengala. Oriented with north to the left. Page number in upper right: 69. Likely from: Thresor De Chartes, Contenant Les Tableaux De Tous Les Pays Du Monde / Barent Langenes. Amsterdam: Christoffle Guyot, 1602. 1 map ; 9 x 13 cm
